data.description: Check out this unique craftsmen-style brick home located on a large corner lot. The main level has a large living room with lots of natural light & a gas fireplace (converted 2019) surrounded by built-in cabinets & shelves. The kitchen features original cabinets & hardware, heated tile floors, & breakfast bar area & opens into the dining room that has plenty of room for large table & buffet. There is a main floor bedroom & full bath with a large built-in cabinet in hallway area. Upstairs has 2 more bedrooms & potential attic storage. One bedroom is used as guest room/office with a built-in desk area. Great potential to refinish the original hardwood floors! Plenty of outdoor spaces to enjoy with a cozy screened-in front porch & back area fenced-in with deck & patio. 2019 updates; new roof(tear-off), walk-in basement shower, radon mitigation. 2020 ceiling fans.
